86
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:52,720
I met you at the wedding.
You're the guy from Ye Meng's blind date.

87
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:54,640
Hello.

88
00:04:57,680 --> 00:05:00,040
It's their gathering.
What are you even doing here?

89
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,240
Come with me.

90
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:04,320
