91
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:06,840
It's nothing urgent, really.

92
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:10,040
I was thinking we should invest
on an education fund for our kid.

93
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:11,320
All my colleagues
are talking about it lately.

94
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:13,080
It got me thinking
we should get one for our son too.

95
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:16,680
Did you come here for the investment,

96
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:18,200
or just to show off your new car?

97
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:21,840
Businesspeople upgrade cars all the time.

98
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:24,760
Ye Meng, since you're friends,
convince her.

99
00:05:24,840 --> 00:05:27,560
Like I said before, blunt but true,

100
00:05:27,640 --> 00:05:29,520
wouldn't a stable option be better?

101
00:05:30,840 --> 00:05:32,000
Not really.

102
00:05:32,080 --> 00:05:34,480
I just hope I can be
Ms. Ye's backup option.

103
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:36,760
If I'm qualified to be her backup,

104
00:05:36,840 --> 00:05:39,160
at least that proves I, Gao Yuan,
am not completely hopeless, right?

105
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:42,520
Come on, Dr. Gao. You're way too humble!
With your credentials, you'd be

106
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:44,520
the top catch in Ningsui's dating scene.

107
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:47,080
Are you done here?

108
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:49,640
If you really want to be a good father,

109
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:51,080
go home and reflect on yourself.

110
00:05:51,640 --> 00:05:53,240
Stop disappearing
every time Jiayu needs you.

111
00:05:54,280 --> 00:05:56,120
Who the hell are you to judge me?

112
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:58,120
