114
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:02,080
Who left their kid home alone?

115
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,960
When did you see me "partying"?

116
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:05,640
I just went out for dinner!

117
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:09,440
- So, it's fine for you to feast and party?
- How dare you lecture me?

118
00:06:09,520 --> 00:06:10,840
Look at this crowd,

119
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,640
eating, drinking, partying!

120
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:13,920
- What is it then?
- Hey, you.

121
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:16,120
Enough with the yapping.

122
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:17,560
Just back off already.

123
00:06:17,640 --> 00:06:18,720
Ugh, you're so annoying.

124
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:20,560
We're just friends having dinner.
Stop killing the mood.

125
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:22,280
Chen Jian,

126
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:24,680
if you want to see the kid,
go to Jiayu's grandma's place.

127
00:06:24,760 --> 00:06:26,200
What are you making a scene here for?

128
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:28,200
Go ahead. Keep hanging out
with these lowlifes.

129
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:29,760
Soon enough, you'll rub off on our son.

130
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,600
Who touched my car?

131
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,440
Who did this?

132
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:40,120
Which son of a bitch was it?

133
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:41,440
Who?

134
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:45,920
Let's go somewhere else to sit.

135
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:49,720
Come over to my place.

136
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:51,000
Sure.

137
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:52,320
- Let's go.
- Go.

138
00:06:53,960 --> 00:06:55,040
Let's go.

139
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:58,760
Car wash fee?

140
00:06:58,840 --> 00:07:00,800
You think I care about your damn money?

141
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:03,880
Audis have four rings, and yours?
Four rotten eggs?

142
00:07:03,960 --> 00:07:04,920
Custom-made?

143
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:10,720
Wash off that egg white already.
Once it dries, you'll never get it off.

144
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,480
Wow, your bar is really nice.

145
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:21,600
It's okay.

146
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:22,720
Maimai!

147
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:24,520
- Maimai.
- Escort them in.

148
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:26,760
Dr. Gao,

149
00:07:26,840 --> 00:07:29,160
order whatever you want today.

150
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:31,800
- It's all on me, the younger guy.
- Fine.

151
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:34,960
- I'll go make a quick call.
- Got it, bro!

152
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:37,520
- Yan'en, Ye Meng! Long time no see!
- Yeah.

153
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:39,520
- Take a seat. I'll grab the drinks menu.
- Fine.

154
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:41,040
I need to use the restroom.

155
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,080
Maimai,

156
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:43,480
what've you been up to lately?

157
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,720
- Wanna do some part-time work?
- Have a seat, Dr. Gao.

158
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:46,440
- Sure! What is it?
- What do you want to drink?

159
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:47,920
- Let me text you on WeChat.
- Fine.

160
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:48,840
Thank you.

161
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,440
Come on.

162
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:59,000
I'll transfer the car wash payment to you.

163
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:03,920
Don't worry about it.

164
00:08:04,520 --> 00:08:06,080
Let's pay separately.
That's what you prefer.

165
00:08:28,400 --> 00:08:29,680
Where were you?

166
00:08:29,760 --> 00:08:31,680
Dr. Gao is here with Ye Meng.

167
00:08:31,760 --> 00:08:33,720
Is this the music you like?

168
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:36,320
I really want to know
what kind of music you're into.

169
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:38,039
No offense,

170
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:41,080
but if you don't make a move soon, you'll
end up being someone else's groomsman.

171
00:08:47,760 --> 00:08:48,880
Dr. Gao,

172
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,400
do you usually work out?

173
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:52,920
As long as there's no surgery,
I make time for it.

174
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:55,640
What about you, Ms. Ye?

175
00:09:01,640 --> 00:09:03,080
He's asking if you work out.

176
00:09:05,160 --> 00:09:06,800
I don't workout much,

177
00:09:06,880 --> 00:09:08,880
but I do go for runs occasionally.

178
00:09:11,520 --> 00:09:13,880
Good evening. Thank you all for coming.

179
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:18,840
Tonight, I'll sing a very special song.

180
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:22,560
One that means a lot to me.

181
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:24,440
It was sung to me by someone important.

182
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:29,400
That night, she was drunk

183
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,520
and said so many drunken words.

184
00:09:32,160 --> 00:09:33,240
Li Jinyu,

185
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:36,240
if anyone ever tells you

186
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:38,640
you're not qualified,

187
00:09:39,280 --> 00:09:40,880
send them to me.

188
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:43,720
From now on,

189
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:47,080
let me conquer the world for you.

190
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:52,160
I wonder if that person

191
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:53,360
still remembers any of it.

192
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:17,240
<i>Your eyes</i>

193
00:10:19,040 --> 00:10:23,840
<i>Like shooting stars in the night</i>

194
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:27,560
<i>Streaking</i>

195
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:32,600
<i>Across frozen borders</i>

196
00:10:33,400 --> 00:10:35,800
<i>To pierce my heart's defenses</i>

197
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:39,520
<i>Just like that, conquered</i>

198
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:45,000
<i>A black goldfish</i>

199
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:51,200
<i>Stranded in desert sands</i>

200
00:10:53,640 --> 00:11:00,560
<i>Even if all memories fade</i>

201
00:11:00,640 --> 00:11:03,760
<i>Your silhouette lingers</i>

202
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:06,480
<i>Etched in my mind</i>

203
00:11:06,560 --> 00:11:10,640
<i>Every time I gaze at you, longing to near</i>

204
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:13,760
<i>I drown, unasked, in reverie</i>

205
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:17,040
<i>Those accidental heartbeats</i>

206
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,880
<i>How could I ever discard them?</i>

207
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:24,680
<i>If you sensed my turmoil, my retreat</i>

208
00:11:24,760 --> 00:11:30,960
<i>Know it's only because I care too deeply</i>
<i>The courage I threw away</i>

209
00:11:31,640 --> 00:11:34,720
<i>Where does it hide now?</i>

210
00:11:34,800 --> 00:11:40,040
<i>With the last of my strength</i>
<i>I'd reach to hold you</i>

211
00:11:40,880 --> 00:11:42,800
<i>Don't you dare doubt it</i>

212
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:47,760
With how Li Jinyu acted today?

213
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:50,600
No doubt about it. He's totally into you.

214
00:11:59,680 --> 00:12:00,680
I'm a bit tired.

215
00:12:02,520 --> 00:12:03,480
I'll head back first.

