00:13:09,640 --> 00:13:11,720
Not going mountain climbing.
I'm exhausted.

223
00:13:11,800 --> 00:13:13,040
Here you go, miss.

224
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:15,400
- Please enjoy your meal.
- Thanks.

225
00:13:20,800 --> 00:13:23,640
The beach sounds alright.
Then, let's go watch the sunset.

226
00:13:53,800 --> 00:13:54,960
What are you doing?

227
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:57,360
I've changed the water for your goldfish.

228
00:13:58,360 --> 00:13:59,200
Who said you could touch it?

229
00:14:00,600 --> 00:14:02,600
This helps them sunbathe properly.

230
00:14:02,680 --> 00:14:04,240
Prevents black spot disease.

231
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:06,640
How can you tell
it has black spot disease?

232
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:08,360
Ye Meng told me.

233
00:14:08,880 --> 00:14:11,840
That day at the bar,
she offered me a side gig.

234
00:14:11,920 --> 00:14:13,640
I thought it was some regular job,

235
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:17,000
but turns out she paid me just
to help you change the goldfish's water

236
00:14:17,080 --> 00:14:18,000
and give them sun.

237
00:14:19,400 --> 00:14:21,680
She said they get black spots

238
00:14:21,760 --> 00:14:23,000
