239
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:24,440
or lack of sunlight.

240
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:29,680
Look.

241
00:14:29,760 --> 00:14:32,760
Just some sunshine and this black fish
is already way more lively.

242
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:36,040
Gotta send Ye Meng a progress report.

243
00:14:38,920 --> 00:14:41,240
