245
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:46,320
Her WeChat Moments are stunning!

246
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:54,200
The beach sounds alright.
Then, let's go watch the sunset.

247
00:15:06,880 --> 00:15:08,360
Hah! Who else but me?

248
00:15:08,880 --> 00:15:09,880
Best wingman ever!

